snippet.title: Shuffled Nightmares v2.0.0 - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
This is my latest puzzle game "Shuffled Nightmares". It is a small-scale 3D puzzle game, where the user is presented to one shuffled image every level. To solve the puzzle the puzzle has to be completely revealed.

You can get the game on Itch.io: https://darkdimension.itch.io/shuffled-nightmares
